    "## Solutions to Differentiation Rules Exercises",
    "",
    "### Exercise 1: Sum Rule",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** d/dx x² + d/dx sin x = 2x + cos x",
    "",
    "**c)** d/dx e^x + d/dx ln x = e^x + 1/x",
    "",
    "**d)** 3x² - 4x + 3",
    "",
    "**e)** -sin x + sec² x",
    "",
    "### Exercise 2: Constant Multiple Rule",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** 5 × 3x² = 15x²",
    "",
    "**c)** -2 × cos x = -2 cos x",
    "",
    "**d)** 3 × e^x = 3 e^x",
    "",
    "**e)** π × 1/x = π/x",
    "",
    "### Exercise 3: Difference Rule",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** 2x + sin x",
    "",
    "**c)** e^x - 3x²",
    "",
    "**d)** 1/x - cos x",
    "",
    "**e)** sec² x - sec x tan x",
    "",
    "### Exercise 4: Product Rule",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** 2x sin x + x² cos x",
    "",
    "**c)** x e^x + e^x = e^x (x + 1)",
    "",
    "**d)** 2x cos x + (x+1) (-sin x) = 2x cos x - (x+1) sin x",
    "",
    "**e)** 2x ln x + x² (1/x) = 2x ln x + x",
    "",
    "### Exercise 5: Quotient Rule",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** (cos x cos x - sin x (-sin x)) / cos² x = (cos² x + sin² x)/cos² x = 1/cos² x = sec² x",
    "",
    "**c)** [(2x)(x+1) - x²(1)]/(x+1)² = (2x² + 2x - x²)/(x+1)² = (x² + 2x)/(x+1)²",
    "",
    "**d)** (e^x x - e^x (1))/x² = e^x (x - 1)/x²",
    "",
    "**e)** [(1)(x+1) - (x-1)(1)]/(x+1)² = (x+1 - x + 1)/(x+1)² = 2/(x+1)²",
    "",
    "### Exercise 6: Chain Rule - Basic",
    "",
    "**a)** Yes",
    "",
    "**b)** cos(x²) × 2x = 2x cos x²",
    "",
    "**c)** e^{x³} × 3x² = 3x² e^{x³}",
    "",
    "**d)** (1/(x² + 1)) × 2x = 2x/(x² + 1)",
    "",
    "**e)** -sin(√x) × (1/(2√x)) = -sin(√x)/(2√x)",
    "",
    "### Exercise 7: Chain Rule - Power Functions",
    "",
    "**a)** 3(x² + 1)^2 × 2x = 6x (x² + 1)^2",
    "",
    "**b)** (1/2)(x³ + 2x)^{-1/2} × (3x² + 2) = (3x² + 2)/(2√(x³ + 2x))",
    "",
    "**c)** 2 sin x × cos x = sin 2x",
    "",
    "**d)** e^{sin x} × cos x",
    "",
    "**e)** (1/cos x) × (-sin x) = -tan x",
    "",
    "### Exercise 8: Chain Rule - Multiple Compositions",
    "",
    "**a)** cos(cos x) × (-sin x) = -sin x cos(cos x)",
    "",
    "**b)** e^{e^x} × e^x = e^x e^{e^x} = e^{e^x + x}",
    "",
    "**c)** (1/ln x) × (1/x) = 1/(x ln x)",
    "",
    "**d)** (1/2)(sin x)^{-1/2} × cos x = cos x / (2 √(sin x))",
    "",
