    "### Exercise 13: Higher Order Derivatives with Rules",
    "",
    "**a)** d/dx (x sin x + cos x) = d/dx (x sin x) + d/dx cos x = (x cos x + sin x) - sin x = x cos x",
    "",
    "**b)** d/dx (x² e^x + 2x e^x) = d/dx (x² e^x) + 2 d/dx (x e^x) = (2x e^x + x² e^x) + 2(x e^x + e^x) = e^x (x² + 2x + 2x + 2) = e^x (x² + 4x + 2)",
    "",
